{"tid":243483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電騙停不了】今年至少有78人中招 一半受害人30歲以下","createTime":"2017-05-14T16:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T05:42:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7edffd055d720d4709bc8a77da2c8f26868b72c8","tid":243483,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170514/large/1494767134_d318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494767134_d318.jpg&h=fc99098c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 3日6宗電騙案，當中5名事主年齡僅得20至28歲，令人關注騙案受害人年輕化問題。據警方統計，今年首季「假冒官員電話騙案」有78人中招，合共被騙去3,703萬元，一半事主是30歲或以下的年輕人，當中不乏擁有大專學歷甚至是專業人士。為何這類人士仍會被老掉了牙的騙術騙倒？有資深警官指原因複雜，原因可能包括他們不喜看新聞、誤信公安萬能、又或是無法抵受騙徒的疲勞轟炸式語言技巧。<br />\n<br />\n警官坦言電話騙徒游說技巧很強，會根據受害人的反應使用不同騙術，例如遇上年紀大的苦主，騙徒會假扮其子女訛稱被綁架或脅持，央求對方盡快到找換店匯錢救人，事實上今年首季18宗虛構綁架騙案的受害人全都超過60歲。<br />\n<br />\n遇到不信虛構綁架的年青及高學歷者，騙徒則會假冒內地公安或入境處人員，恫嚇事主指他涉經濟犯案，並會用Wechat等展示受害人相片甚至虛構的法律文件，令事主相信已被公安調查，騙徒又會禁止事主「收線」，一直疲勞轟炸到對方崩潰願付款為止。若受害人碰巧是內地出生的新移民或交流生，又或是因長期在內地生活或經商致誤信公安萬能，即較易中招。今年首季78名電騙受害人有一半在30歲或以下，當中九成損失(3,341萬元)都來自擁有高中甚至大專學歷的苦主。<br />\n<br />\n因應年青一族慣用手機，騙徒甚至撰寫了手機黑客程式，以助盜取受害人手機內的網銀密碼以非法轉移存款，防不勝防。立法會保安事務委員會委員林卓廷議員指，電話騙案禁之不絕，可能與騙術不斷進化及受害人不願看新聞有關，他稱唯有靠加強中港警方合作，才能對付跨境騙徒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170514/56693886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170514%2F56693886&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dbbc3d51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170514%2F56693886&h=f6aa9c94\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170514/56693886</a>"},{"pid":"e72d60f22e51279f263a3fe07350af88344ad7cb","tid":243483,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"所謂三十以下，九成九咪匪蟈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb046e2e90a21ffd69610c3c24f1f7936e68932","tid":243483,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"依家啲友講廣東話會收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94875ad0a294e9da8133f984771a8dbc932b551e","tid":243483,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Aq4wqWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAq4wqWv.png&h=f0dcebb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2397b78e7564e8ff90977acca4e55b57db03939f","tid":243483,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"已經通天又通天，仲有咁多蠢柒柒<br />\n呢D人絕對適合人道毀滅<br />\n咁撚蠢唔死都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b337dce91f504c9777c940d8f28027ad1d049373","tid":243483,"uid":38609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔寫埋幾多係蝗國人？"},{"pid":"9dc4455e678b6b811037cb605dc4a72085a400db","tid":243483,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家啲友講廣東話會收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經識聽四字真言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b197db9ceb94acfbb342d1ab56af9d9d1b063258","tid":243483,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經通天又通天，仲有咁多蠢柒柒<br />\n呢D人絕對適合人道毀滅<br />\n咁撚蠢唔死都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"